It is quite remarkable how well he manages his work. My father has had wisdom tooth pain for quite sometime, but it is now extracted because of Dr. Pagare's professional approach and kind manner. Throughout his treatment, his empathetic attention and openness to listening were invaluable. Doctor is very friendly and explained everything about treatment in detail. I was feeling relaxed throughout the procedure as light music was played in background. Overall it's a great experience. Highly recommendable..true perfectionist!

I am someone who does not believe in healing with the doctors and dentists scare me the most 😂 Yet I've been a client of Doc Rahul for a really long time! He's really great at giving that safe space, where I'm able to relax and mentally prepare myself for the dental work. I've visited him for tooth removals, fillings, route canals. The best thing is that he has a really light hand meaning his work doesn't hurt the teeth, the anesthesia doesn't hurt.
Recently I had my son visit him too for dental cap on two of his front teeth. Doc Rahul gave a huge list of options to choose from. That's the thing, he always provides all of the options available along with their pros and cons and gives us the space to decide what would work, all the time recommending the best option too!
The whole time, we'd been thinking my son needs dental caps. But when the doc actually inspected his teeth, he recommended dental fillings. The reason being my son is too young and he found it wrong somewhere to do such major work on him.Even though the cost of dental fillings were a lot less....see this is the thing. We dont find many doctors who work with such integrity and give preference to the client's well being instead of their own profit! Doc Rahul is one of them! 
I'd definitely recommend him to anyone who is concerned with their dental health. He is knowledgeable, prompt, works at the deepest level and doesn't charge much for the kind of service he offers!

My Daughter have been a client of Dr. Rahul pagare for a really long time. My Daughter's teeth were not in proper placement for that we took appointment from Dr. Rahul pagare. He really gave us good advices and did a good treatment to my daughter. During treatment, I was extremely worried about my daughter's teeth coz she had a lot of gap between every teeth. Amazingly Dr. Rahul pagare did cover all the gaps and fixed every teeth properly Now my daughter's treatment is over and I am really satisfied with the results. 😊
